<li id="cite_note-inquiry_discredits-12"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-inquiry_discredits_12-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-inquiry_discredits_12-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation news"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1951/12/22/121446103.pdf">"Inquiry Discredit O'Dwyer for Calling Reles Important"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. <i>New York Times</i>. December 22, 1951<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">31 December</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=New+York+Times&amp;rft.atitle=Inquiry+Discredit+O%27Dwyer+for+Calling+Reles+Important&amp;rft.date=1951-12-22&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Ftimesmachine.nytimes.com%2Ftimesmachine%2F1951%2F12%2F22%2F121446103.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAlbert+Anastasia" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/></span>
</li>
